{
  "stem": "304.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So those were two sisters in a different approach to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] sister.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What-- what do you-- what do you think brought Itel to this kind of behavior?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It brought her to the behavior because we were taught to stay in line and to get a dress.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not supposed to go again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we told her, but you gave mother such as small dress.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't care.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She acted-- at that point, she acted like the Germans, and she didn't have to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at that time that she came, it was terrible, so the jealousy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she let out her jealousy to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't have anybody else to let it out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she let it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think people react on bad experiences in life in two ways.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or they are kinder to other people afterwards, because they-- what they went through, or they want to pay back to somebody else.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think she belonged to those who wanted to pay back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was my worst experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have too-- too many wrong because I usually was very careful to-- with me-- my behavior.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was really, except one time, never singled out on my own to-- to have punishment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But once, when I volunteered to go to-- to-- for some kind of work, I was taken to-- this was already in the second camp-- I was taken to Leipzig to pick up something on trucks.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I succeeded to grab some potatoes that I put in-- under my dress.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we came back to camp, I ran to my barracks to hide it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I came back, the SS woman saw me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, where did you go?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
